n this list, <a data-i13n="cpos:84;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Humble Bundle;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8cce7f0e-1975-4189-ad0c-2981dc30d13c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Humble+Bundle&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4Y2NlN2YwZS0xOTc1LTQxODktYWQwYy0yOTgxZGMzMGQxM2MiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaHVtYmxlYnVuZGxlLmNvbS9zdG9yZS96ZW4tYm91bmQtMiIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZDJjOGIxY2ItMzg0ZS00NzY1LTg0N2QtODI3ZmQ1NDdlZTI2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAdpO6MbfElGNlZpyj0E5WUYaIaluRvh6-02EET6OL3VH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Fzen-bound-2"><em>Zen Bound 2</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> has a simple premise: You get a rope and a series of 3D sculptures, and your goal is to wrap the rope around each sculpture until it&#39;s covered completely, coating it with paint in the process. The sculptures themselves can be more difficult than they first seem, however, with many hidden gaps and sharp angles.</p><p> Playing <em>Zen Bound 2</em> demands slow contemplation, almost like meditating on the object you&#39;re binding. This, in turn, may lead you to reflect on the physical nuances of the <em>things</em> you tie yourself to in real life. But even if that sounds pompous, just know that <em>Zen Bound 2</em> offers a thoughtful way to zone out.</p><p> <strong>Buy for</strong> : <a data-i13n="cpos:85;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Nintendo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=21fc7c82-c5eb-49a9-b5d3-fc32a78290de&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Nintendo&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIyMWZjN2M4Mi1jNWViLTQ5YTktYjVkMy1mYzMyYTc4MjkwZGUiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmludGVuZG8uY29tL3N0b3JlL3Byb2R1Y3RzL3plbi1ib3VuZC0yLXN3aXRjaC8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQyYzhiMWNiLTM4NGUtNDc2NS04NDdkLTgyN2ZkNTQ3ZWUyNiJ9&amp;signature=AQ